# Next.js Frontend

## Route groups & themes (already in repo)

| Group | `data-theme` |
|---|---|
| `(gift)`, `(blog)`, commerce/editorial/platform admin | `gift` |
| `(creator)`, creator admin | `creator` |

Set theme on the **layout** wrapper (`apps/web/app/(gift)/layout.tsx` pattern). Never import Soft Gift pink tokens into creator routes (or vice versa).

## Rendering

| Default | When to break |
|---|---|
| Server Component | Read pages, SEO content, catalog |
| `'use client'` island | Cart interactions, forms, GSAP, drawers |

- No JWT secrets / payment keys in client bundles (`NEXT_PUBLIC_*` only when truly public).
- Prefer Nest `/api/v1` as source of truth. Add Next route handlers only when BFF is justified.
- Server Actions (if used) = **same Zod + AuthZ bar as Nest** — not a backdoor.

## State & forms

- Server state: TanStack Query. Local UI: React state.
- Forms: RHF + Zod. Disable submit while in-flight on pay / proposal / publish.
- Critical controls: `data-testid` kebab-case (`checkout-pay-button`).
- Field errors inline; toasts (Sonner) for transient issues; keep form values on recoverable failure.
- Hiding an admin nav link ≠ authorization.

## Motion

GSAP for Soft Gift marketing/PDP/builder storytelling (`15-gsap-motion`). Checkout/cart/admin → crisp, almost no motion. Framer only for tiny presence UI.
